<h2 id="openrouter-model-scout" style="margin:16px 0 8px">openrouter-model-scout</h2>
<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Tests free model availability on OpenRouter platform.</p>
<p><strong>Found:</strong> Only 2 out of 6 free models are currently operational. Gemma-3-4b-it and Gemma-3-12b-it are working with response times of 1030ms and 5466ms respectively. Mistral-small, Qwen3 models, and DeepSeek-R1 are all returning errors - either provider errors or missing endpoints entirely.</p>

<h2 id="free-stuff-radar" style="margin:16px 0 8px">free-stuff-radar</h2>
<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Scans Craigslist free section for furniture, electronics, tools, and appliances.</p>
<p><strong>Found:</strong> 27 items discovered in Inland Empire with strong furniture selection (10 furniture + 8 desk hits). Notable finds include four large filing cabinets in Victorville, a 6-person Catalina Spas hot tub in Temecula, and a Sony receiver in Yucaipa. Heavy concentration of office furniture and storage solutions available.</p>
