<h2 id="foreclosure-monitor" style="margin:16px 0 8px">foreclosure-monitor</h2>
<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Searches HUD homes and Fannie Mae listings for foreclosures in 25-mile radius.</p>
<p><strong>Found:</strong> All major sources returned errors or empty results. HUD HomeStore returned HTTP 404, Fannie Mae HomePath loaded but had no parseable listings, and Craigslist REO search found no results. The sites appear to require browser-based access rather than direct scraping.</p>

