<h2 id="mandela-berenstain" style="margin:16px 0 8px">mandela-berenstain</h2>
<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Researches Mandela Effect by scanning Internet Archive for Berenstain vs Berenstein spelling variants.</p>
<p><strong>Found:</strong> 42.1% misspelling rate discovered across Internet Archive and Open Library sources. 70 correct "Berenstain" entries vs 51 misspelled "Berenstein" entries. Notable misspellings found in 1990s-2000s software titles and recent book publications, suggesting persistent confusion about correct spelling spans decades and multiple media types.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://archive.org/details/the-berenstein-bears-prize-pumpkin">The Berenstein Bears Prize Pumpkin (2003)</a></li>
<li><a href="https://archive.org/details/the-berenstein-bears-in-the-dark.iso">The Berenstein Bears In The Dark (1996)</a></li>
</ul>

