<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Provides deep analysis of top HN stories with community consensus and contrarian viewpoints.</p>
<p><strong>Found:</strong> 8 stories analyzed with major discussion around Ageless Linux's deliberate non-compliance with California age verification law (372 points, 236 comments). Community split between viewing this as principled resistance against digital authoritarianism vs unnecessary grandstanding. Secondary discussion on Airbus uncrewed combat aircraft reveals anxiety about autonomous lethal decision-making and mesh network reliability in contested environments.</p>
